{"tid":1494766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知SAYA_SHAN而家點?","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T00:33:34.000Z","uid":172172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5276195e1c5aee3de92057f9efa16f9c2d344e0f","tid":1494766,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"四川大地震香港女生幸災樂禍事件是2008年四川大地震的衍生事件。一名香港屯門保良局董玉娣中學女生因為在網誌上寫了一些不尊重四川災民的言論，引起網民非議，被一眾網民怒罵及咀咒。事主的相片曝光之後，她更被網民稱為港女。<br />\n<br />\n之後事主因為遭其他網友起底，而決定在網誌上道歉，並刪除之前在網誌上的「冷血言論」。[1]不過，有關的言論卻一早已被其他網民備份，即使事主道歉，也改變不了被一些網民的觀感。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港新浪網的投票，太多數的網民都認為事主「沒家教」。<br />\n<br />\n直到2008年5月18日晚上，事主 SAYA_SHAN 再公開道歉，以平息一些網民的怒火。不過，有網友看完她在 qooza blog 裡的網誌之後，都仍然沒有原諒她。<br />\n<br />\n最後，事主 SAYA_SHAN 被懷疑已經再次「潛水」，而校方亦已經在2008年5月26日記事主一個大過。"},{"pid":"bd48863c01aca7f4957f344e29088e7e89e5c97c","tid":1494766,"uid":138860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T20:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99d151c2b80fe5750208bd8c48348fd20fee7724","tid":1494766,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T21:15:26.000Z","msg":"先知少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dadec18f79d4d80ad79da564a4026688a801966a","tid":1494766,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T21:18:21.000Z","msg":"咁都記得大過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d8bd92104431d60fdc5de560adf9c834dd3000","tid":1494766,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99d151c2b80fe5750208bd8c48348fd20fee7724","tid":1494766,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T21:15:26.000Z","msg":"先知少女<img src=\"/ass